{"type":"message","id":"d823a740","parentId":"85d3f05a","timestamp":"2026-03-24T16:48:45.764Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_nwckc6ni95db_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 4626\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='research/cfi_hybrid_experiment.ps1' new_len=1821\n[mutation proposed] research/cfi_hybrid_experiment.ps1\n[master db17291] pulse: 2026-03-24 124817\n 6 files changed, 289 insertions(+), 78 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 124817.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 124817.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 124316.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 124817 - The CFI Compression Synthesis has identified the \"Constant Format Problem\" and derived a concrete three-dimensional filter formula: score(T) = CFI(T) x min(1, freq(T)/120). The next logical step is to implement Strategy C (hybrid scoring) and compare it against the freq-only and CFI-hard baselines already tested."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"young-bloom","total":9,"totalLines":9,"totalChars":833,"truncated":false,"exitCode":0,"name":"powershell C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774370925762}}
